officially certified by the authorities to produce AI vaccines, is to be
found in 20051126.3431. We are aware of unofficial but generally reliable
information about the activity of (between 10 and 30) additional,
uncertified plants. One might hope that the Chinese authorities are taking
the necessary steps to remedy this undesirable situation. - Mod.AS]
